L_PORT_NO_PREAUTH ]: disable pre-auth over nl80211 control port support\r\n\t\t* [ PROTECTED_TWT ]: protected Target Wake Time (TWT) support\r\n\t\t* [ DEL_IBSS_STA ]: deletion of IBSS station support\r\n\t\t* [ BEACON_PROTECTION_CLIENT ]: beacon prot. for clients support\r\n\t\t* [ SCAN_FREQ_KHZ ]: scan on kHz frequency support\r\n\t\t* [ CONTROL_PORT_OVER_NL80211_TX_STATUS ]: tx status for nl80211 contr"]
